<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Appointment Letter</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Calibri', Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #000;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .page {
      width: 210mm;
      height: 297mm;
      padding: 40mm 25mm 25mm 25mm;
      position: relative;
      page-break-after: always;
    }

    .letterhead {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 210mm;
      height: auto;
    }

    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 210mm;
      height: auto;
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .title {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: underline;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .date {
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    p {
      text-align: justify;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .sub {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    ol {
      padding-left: 18px;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .signature-block {
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .signature-block img {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .stamp {
      width: 100px;
      position: absolute;
      right: 70px;
      bottom: 60px;
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    .salary-table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 80%;
      margin: 25px auto;
    }

    .salary-table th,
    .salary-table td {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .salary-table th {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .annexure-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: left;
      width: 85%;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .note ul {
      padding-left: 18px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- PAGE 1 -->
  <div class="page">
    <% if (letterheadPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= letterheadPath %>" class="letterhead" alt="Letterhead" />
    <% } %>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="date"><%= new Date(appointmentDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %></p>

      <p class="title">Letter of Appointment</p>

      <p>To,<br/>
        <%= employeeName %>,<br/>
        <%= address %>.
      </p>

      <p>Dear <%= employeeName.split(" ")[0] %>,</p>

      <p class="sub">Sub: Your Career with AMAZON IT SOLUTIONS.</p>

      <p>We are immensely pleased to appoint you as a <strong><%= designation %></strong>, and have you as part of Amazon IT Solutions family. We believe your potential skills will be a valuable contribution to our company.</p>

      <p><strong>Effective Date of Appointment:</strong> Your date of joining at “Amazon IT Solutions” is <%= new Date(joiningDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %> and the following are the terms and conditions:</p>

      <ol start="1">
        <li><strong>Job Assignment:</strong> You will be required to perform duties as laid down in the Job Description for your position.</li>
        <li><strong>Leave Entitlement:</strong> You will be entitled to leaves as per Amazon IT Solutions policy mentioned in Rules and Regulations formulated in the Employee Handbook of Amazon IT Solutions from time to time.</li>
        <li><strong>Placement & Compensation:</strong> You will be placed in the appropriate responsibility level and will be entitled to total compensation of INR <%= ctcAnnual.toLocaleString('en-IN') %> (<%= ctcWords %>) per annum. Compensation will be governed by company rules. Note: The breakup of the fixed salary is as per the annexure sheet.</li>
        <li><strong>Statutory Deductions:</strong> Deductions, if any, will be made from your salary as per prevailing laws.</li>
        <li><strong>Code of Conduct:</strong> You are expected to ensure compliance with company policies and ethics.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <% if (footerPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= footerPath %>" class="footer" alt="Footer" />
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 2 -->
  <div class="page">
    <% if (letterheadPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= letterheadPath %>" class="letterhead" alt="Letterhead" />
    <% } %>
    <div class="content">
      <ol start="6">
        <li><strong>Posting & Transfer:</strong> Your initial posting will be at Hyderabad. However, your services are liable to be transferred...</li>
        <li><strong>Probation:</strong> You will be on probation for a period of six months...</li>
        <li><strong>Full-time Employment:</strong> Your position is a full-time employment...</li>
        <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> You shall not, during or after employment, share company information...</li>
        <li><strong>Intellectual Property:</strong> Any invention or idea developed during employment shall belong to the company...</li>
        <li><strong>Past Records:</strong> Any misrepresentation of facts may lead to termination...</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <% if (footerPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= footerPath %>" class="footer" alt="Footer" />
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 3 -->
  <div class="page">
    <% if (letterheadPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= letterheadPath %>" class="letterhead" alt="Letterhead" />
    <% } %>
    <div class="content">
      <ol start="12">
        <li><strong>Termination of Employment:</strong> Services can be terminated by giving notice or salary in lieu...</li>
        <li><strong>General Conditions:</strong> You shall be bound by all applicable rules and regulations of the company.</li>
        <li><strong>Absence from Duty:</strong> Absence without reason for more than three days will be treated as abandonment...</li>
        <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> You must not disclose company secrets at any point...</li>
        <li><strong>Acceptance:</strong> If you accept the terms, please sign and return a copy of this letter...</li>
      </ol>

      <div class="signature-block">
        <p>For Amazon IT Solutions</p>
        <% if (signaturePath) { %>
          <img src="<%= signaturePath %>" alt="Signature" />
        <% } %>
        <p><%= hrName %></p>
        <p><strong><%= hrDesignation %></strong></p>
      </div>

      <% if (stampPath) { %>
        <img src="<%= stampPath %>" class="stamp" alt="Company Stamp" />
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <% if (footerPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= footerPath %>" class="footer" alt="Footer" />
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 4: Annexure -->
  <div class="page">
    <% if (letterheadPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= letterheadPath %>" class="letterhead" alt="Letterhead" />
    <% } %>
    <div class="content">
      <p style="text-align:center; font-size:13px;">
        Note: This is a computer-generated document. No Signature is required.
      </p>

      <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:15px;">
        This is to certify that I, <strong><%= employeeName %></strong>, have read and understood all the above-mentioned terms and conditions and accept them.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:30px; text-align:center;">
        Date: ____________ &nbsp;&nbsp; Place: ____________ &nbsp;&nbsp; Signature: ____________
      </p>

      <p class="annexure-title">Annexure - I</p>

      <table class="salary-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Components</th>
            <th>Per annum</th>
            <th>Per month</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% salaryBreakdown.forEach((item) => { %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= item.component %></td>
              <td><%= item.annualAmount.toLocaleString('en-IN') %></td>
              <td><%= item.monthlyAmount.toLocaleString('en-IN') %></td>
            </tr>
          <% }) %>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <div class="note">
        <p><strong>Note:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Medical Insurance covers Rs.4 Lakhs for the employee and dependents.</li>
          <li>Personal Accident Insurance covers Rs.7.5 Lakhs for the employee.</li>
          <li>LTA can be claimed at the end of the financial year as per Income Tax Act provisions.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if (footerPath) { %>
      <img src="<%= footerPath %>" class="footer" alt="Footer" />
    <% } %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
